						               													<description>Implosion is a middle weight euro-style dice game takes place in a sci-fi fantasy world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played in six rounds. Every round we salvage from an imploding dying star - a set of face-up cards placed in a circle on the table, with dice of different colours and values on them. Players take turns choose dice from the dying star in an Azul-like manner. After that, they will use the dice to generate resources, build cards into their tableaus, and use the dice to trigger the cards' abilities.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can build armies to fight invaders from outer space, sell resources for points, or construct wonders for a lot of rewards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends after the sixth round. Every player sum up their VP token and VPs printed on the cards in their tableau, the one with the most points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
